::EndBringer/Incarcinator/Scyther/Demise::

EndBringer reaches the training room, deciding that he didn't want to train afterall. He hears some voices nearby (Prebon), and walks over to investigate.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Not seeing anyone at the mess hall, Demise walks over to get something to drink. (Anyone want an interesting conversation with a bot that's as dumb as a rock, he's waitin')
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator relaxes in the CR, letting it heal him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Sitting down at a chair, Scyther begins to watch the scanners.
